# Tell it to me straight Jack 
> I don't need 10k widgets, I need 1 good widget I can use 10k times. 

The idea of this section is...start here if you don't have another educated opinion.

Phone Wallet for ZEC Everyday Use + Spending -> [Zashi](https://electriccoin.co/zashi/)

Phone Wallet for minor holdings Everyday Use -> [Edge](https://edge.app/)

For hardware wallets for larger + longterm holdings -> [Ledger](https://www.ledger.com/)

For browser-based Wallet for applications, defi, signing -> [Metamask](https://metamask.io/)

For KYC on-off-ramp fiat to crypto web -> [Kraken](https://www.kraken.com/)

For off-ramping crypto to goods/services -> [Bitrefill](https://www.bitrefill.com/us/en/)

For IRA/401k self-custody wallet + tax handling -> [iTrustCapital](https://itrustcapital.com/?referral_id=b7w8sm&utm_source=RAF)

For secure browsing of the internet for average users (porn/torrent) -> [Tor](https://www.torproject.org/download/)

For secure browsing + VPN for advanced or targeted users -> [Nym](https://nym.com/)

For password manager that doesn't require annual fee -> [Bitwarden](https://bitwarden.com/)